1- khabib is trembling :-)

the only 2 who want this rematch are conor for his ego and dana for his bank account.

masvidal have destroyed nate from A to Z.
nate has dropped on his back several times cause he was near K.O.
the doctor stopped the fight cause nate's face was starting to look like elephantman movie
and the next 2 last rounds would have been more damages on nate body and a 100 % sure K.O.
We were robbed of nothing. Masvidal won cause he was a much better fighter on that night,
and is a much better fighter than nate in general. he is more explosive, faster, more precise has better boxing and kicks.
it's good they stopped it for the sake of Nate's health.
and a rematch would have same outcome, ko or tko.
period
